My friend Joe is a sagittarius whereas his girlfriend is an aries. He's faithful to her and would never cheat on her. Do you believe in horoscope? What zodiac sign are you? I'm a Sagittarius. Tell me about the disposition and personality traits that are typical of a sagittarius. I want to see if they're accurate. Joe is a pianist. His cousin has a bassoon exam soon. She wants Joe to accompany her free of charge. He isn't sure if he wants to do it but he doesn't want her to feel like the rug is bring pulled out from under her. I complimented him on his piano skills. He then said "yes what can I say?" He was late as he got off at the wrong stop and had to wait for another bus. I asked "how on earth did you miss your stop?" He said "im sorry. What can I say?" The current situation is very bad. I said "well yes what can I say?" I was shocked when I saw a car crash on the street. He said "I can imagine" His girlfriend said "I'm sure you were" Joe isn't very well-to-do while his girlfriend's family is very well-off. He held a party at his place yesterday in which cheap wine was served.The sofas in his flat are made of some cheap materials. His television is cheap and nasty. Recently he got lots of clothes on the cheap as the shop is about to go into liquidation. He bought a pair of cheap shoes that felt apart after a couple months so I bought him some good quality shoes. He's too cheap to buy new shoes. He's very mean with the air conditioner too- it's only on for an hour each day then he turns on the fans and opens the windows instead. He vacationed in Macau last week but he's so mean he didnt even buy is postcards. He stayed at a four star hotel that serves cheap and cheerful food and sells cheap and cheerful clothes. He performed Haydn in the party. After that he  explained to us "this passage should be played beautifully rather than rhythmically. Otherwise it's a bit cheap." He asked me to get some Haydn scores for him as I can get them on the cheap from a friend of mine. We watched a kickboxing fight in which Jack hit James with a cheap shot after he lost to James. We watched John vs Anthony as well. The referee could've stopped the fight which would've been a cheap triumph for anthony but fortunately the referee didn't. We also watched a comedy show which was full of cheap laughs. The comedian is famous for his vulgar manner. In the show his suit was vulgar. His jokes and jibes are cheap and vulgar. Today dogs certainly don't come cheap. Ken bought me a steinway for my birthday. Steinway pianos don't come cheap.
